	   <tr><td colspan=2>Has anyone ever got kicked out of a group for picking the mobs pockets clean? I try not to pp too much, but in Rathe Mountains you can steal up to 15pp at a time...its just too damn tempting!<br><br><br><br><br>Woniwilly<br>31 season Rogue-torvonn.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
